<topic id="lyRauschen">
  <title>Damage, Dirt, Stains, Noise (NoiseRegion)</title>
  <body>
    <p>Damage, dirt, stains and other artefacts caused by various factors (e.g. lighting,
            reflections, scanning) must be marked with the <tt>NoiseRegion</tt>. Being marked this
            way, they are not used for text recognition during the training process.</p>
